預兆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/04/30/a102567915.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F04%2F30%2Fa102567915.html&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1deKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=22e4a800\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/04/30/a102567915.html</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T19:30:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國</span></strong><br />\n官民對立，社會動蕩。<br />\n<strong>冇</strong><br />\n思想混亂，人心浮動。<br />\n<strong>中</strong><br />\n加強社會各方控制。<br />\n<strong>中</strong><br />\n亂加稅收，橫征暴斂。<br />\n<strong>冇</strong><br />\n亂發紙幣。貨幣快速貶值。<br />\n<strong>中</strong><br />\n上層醉生夢死，下層苦不堪言。<br />\n<strong>中</strong><br />\n體制僵化，不思進變。<br />\n<strong>中</strong><br />\n中下層失去上升空間。上層斷絕中下層進取之路。<br />\n<strong>中</strong><br />\n：軍隊腐敗，士氣低迷，貪生怕死。<br />\n<strong>中</strong><br />\n粉飾太平，歌功頌德。<br />\n<strong>中</strong><br />\n中國亡國不遠了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T19:37:46.000Z","msg":"之前四川因為黑心飯盒都有官民對立 應該成日都有發生 係一定會封鎖消息我地唔知姐<br />\n<br />\n結論：希望訓醒就滅亡啦"},{"pid":"0a543b993042265b2539c153da6e596ae5fa0dff","tid":1132886,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T21:44:17.000Z","msg":"以前有冇核蛋先"},{"pid":"a12284bc7fb78378002dbae9cea11b27f6b7a15b","tid":1132886,"uid":294,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"acd9599355fcf52217bbc69958b0824d7e4f59a0","tid":1132886,"uid":15984,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T21:47:47.000Z","msg":"聽日就支爆<br />\n連登仔又贏"},{"pid":"94f4aa8b09366008a83fb965f49a5317410845bf","tid":1132886,"uid":47147,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T22:0